Below test cases were added to validate if Pipelines is setting the build URL properly when publishing BuildInfo to Artifactory.

testcase.class: GENERIC_BASH - 4 out of 7 - build info url tests Below test cases were added to validate if Pipelines is setting the build URL properly when publishing BuildInfo to Artifactory. Validate Build Info URL S_BuildInfoUrl_0001. BuildInfo published from a step using the JFrog CLI must have the build URL set with the step URL when JFROG_CLI_BUILD_URL environment variable is not set as part of the step execution.
